thread.title: White House says Obama feels urgency to address U.S. debt limit
thread.title_full: White House says Obama feels urgency to address U.S. debt limit | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: White House says Obama feels urgency to address U.S. debt limit
text:
WASHINGTON Oct 22 Asked about the U.S. Treasury Department's decision to postpone the debt auction over debt limit concerns, White House spokesman Eric Schultz said on Thursday President Barack Obama feels an urgency to address the U.S. debt limit.
(Reporting by Julia Edwards ; Editing by Will Dunham )
